snippet.textDisplay:
This order of events just happened....

Got onto YouTube because I was bored, went onto the trending page because I was super bored, saw this video, remembered how much I love Fluffy, didn’t even know he was going on tour until the end of the video, anxiously waited to see if my city was on the list at the end, noticed it was, went online to see if I could get tickets, tickets are sold out, looks for next closest city, finds tickets, buys tickets, calls sister and informs her we are going on a road trip.
